snippet.title: S8E6 | Virender Sehwag | Breakfast with Champions ft Gaurav Kapur | @skodaindia     ​
snippet.description:
The season finale of ŠKODA presents Breakfast with Champions ft. Gaurav Kapur has some royal swag! 🏏🌟 Say hello to The Nawab of Najafgarh, The Sultan of Multan. 👑

Virender Sehwag is a born entertainer and he continues to enthrall us with his take on his teammates and stories that are now cricketing folklore. From scooter rides with Ashish Nehra to pranking Sourav Ganguly, and from farm fresh buffalo milk to fine dining that Sachin introduced him to, this episode is a rollercoaster of laughter and nostalgia. 

Hear all about his banter with Shoaib Akhtar and the love he got from Pakistani shopkeepers, the invaluable advice Tiger Pataudi's gave him, how he had to return from the airport before his debut and the epic moment he scored 300 runs with a sensational six! 

This episode tastes best with garma-garam desi ghee ke Chole Bhature with Lassi in a kulhad.

snippet.title: #Video नाच रे पतरकी ३.0 | #Arvind Akela Kallu | #Shilpi Raj | Naach Re Patarki 3.0 | #Namrita Malla
snippet.description:
अब होगा चारों ओर हाहाकार #ArvindAkelaKallu & #ShilpiRaj मचाएंगे बवाल...फिर एक बार ! रहs तैयार 

Credits:
🎙Singer - Arvind Akela Kallu & Shilpi Raj
💃Feat - Namrita Malla
✍Writer - Ashutosh Tiwari
🎶Music - Priyanshu Singh
🎥Video By - Team Sanju
🙏EP - Sitosh Yadav
✂Edit - P. Shubham Babu
💃Choreographer - Lakkie Vishwakarma
🎥DOP - Mahesh Venkat
🌈DI - Rohit Singh
🎬Production - Akash Vishwakarma
💃Dance Group - Vicky Francis

📷 BTS - Riyaz Ali

Lyrics:
लड़की :- पागल भइल बाड़ हमरा तू पीछे
आँखे से ला..ग तार फोटो खींचे
ताक जनि आइसे,लागी ईहा पईसे
कमर हिलाइब सगुन प
लड़का:- तोहार तन डोले,तोहार मन डोले
हमार फन डोले,नागिन के धुन प.....

लड़की:- बाबू मछरी के बड़ा सवखिन लागेल
देशी दरुआ के साथे नमकीन मांगे ल
लड़का:- जब लागेलु अईठे कमर,करेजा लाग तारू एक नमर
नजर से बान मारेलु,पतरको जान मारेलु....
लड़की:- धीरे धीरे हँस के,धर तार कस के
आईल बाड़ का हनीमून प
लड़का:- तोहार तन डोले,तोहार मन डोले
हमार फन डोले,नागिन के धुन प.....

लड़की:- देह छुआला प लाग जाला आग जइसे
एह बकरी प टूट जनि बाघ जइसे
लड़का:- जब बाजे ला नागिन गाना,त पागल होला पूरा समियाना
कि पब्लिक नोट फेंकेला, त कलुआ कोट फेंकेला
लड़की:- पंकज आशु बदरी प्रियांशु,माजा ल नाया ट्यून प
लड़का:- तोहार तन डोले,तोहार मन डोले
हमार फन डोले,नागिन के धुन प.....

Episode 3788: Pyarelal's Dilemma
--------------------------------------------------------
Pyaarelal gets into trouble as Sapna and Kalpana have accepted his proposal to get married. Earlier Sapna had not revealed her decision while Babita and Madhavi had asked Pyaarelal to accept Kalpana. As everyone discusses the matter at Popatlal's house, Dr. Hathi comes excited to his house. he announces that they have brought him another proposal for marriage. Anjali and Taarak discuss who will tell the truth to Sapna's family, he calls Sapna's mother but she thinks it to be a prank. Keep an eye out!

About the show:

Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. snippet.title: Tere Bin Episode 51 Teaser - 1st June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Tere Bin Episode 51 Teaser - 1st June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma
Sohail Sameer as Anwar
Sabeena Farooq as Haya
Hira Soomro as Maryam
Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra
Mahmood Aslam as Malik Mukhtaar
Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.title: क्या Bhide का Cooker हो गया Blast? | Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Bhide Ka Cooker
snippet.description:
Click here  to Subscribe to the LIV Comedy channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCpEhnqL0y41EpW2TvWAHD7Q?sub_confirmation=1

Popatlal is stuck on the balcony. Bhide and Madhavi are stuck outside and are worried about the cooker that is on the gas. Both of them don't have the key. Will Sodhi break the door? Will Daya give some solution? Watch the full episode to find out. Stay tuned to unfold the drama.  

Show Name - Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast - Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt
Episode - 1993
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi, Neela Asit Modi

#taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #tmkoc #taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah #livcomedy #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा 
 
About The Show:
----------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a comedy show inspired by the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada Family which consists of uneducated businessmen Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal’s Wife Daya & their naughty Son Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society' and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. In case of a problem and emergency, Jethalal Gada often rushes to Taarak Mehta to seek his help and guidance as he finds a philosopher in him. The housing society residents help each other find solutions when facing common, real-life challenges and getting involved in sticky situations.

Watch special videos of 'Bhide Bana Crorepati':
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLSXTaG1fT0cSCH5ciwJoKjs1SCjN150tq

snippet.description:

Tere Bin Episode 50 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream - 1st June 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally Presented by Jhalak Beauty Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi

snippet.description:
Asur 2 Web Series Review By Deeksha Sharma. snippet.title: Odisha Coromandel Express Train Accident Video | యాక్సిడెంట్ ఇలా జరిగింది లైవ్ వీడియో | RTV
snippet.description:
Odisha Coromandel Express Train Accident Video | యాక్సిడెంట్ ఇలా జరిగింది లైవ్ వీడియో | RTV

కోరమాండల్ ఎక్స్‌ప్రెస్ మరియు బెంగళూరు-హౌరా సూపర్‌ఫాస్ట్ ఎక్స్‌ప్రెస్ ప్రమాదం ఎలా జరిగిందో RTV లైవ్ చూపెట్టే ప్రయత్నం చేసింది . కోరమాండల్ ఎక్స్‌ప్రెస్ పశ్చిమ బెంగాల్ మరియు చెన్నైలోని బెంగాల్ షాలిమార్ స్టేషన్ మధ్య నడుస్తుంది. బహనాగా రైల్వే స్టేషన్ సమీపంలో ఈ ఘర్షణ చోటు చేసుకుంది, దీని ఫలితంగా ప్రయాణికులలో గణనీయమైన సంఖ్యలో ప్రాణనష్టం జరిగింది. ఒ

RTV Live tried to show how the Coromandel Express and Bengaluru-Howrah Superfast Express accidents happened. Coromandel Express runs between Bengal Shalimar station in West Bengal and Chennai. The clash took place near Bahanaga railway station, resulting in the loss of a significant number of passengers.

snippet.title: Bollywood Item Songs की सच्चाई देख लो | @SambhavnaSethEntertainment | Josh Talks Hindi
snippet.description:
Sambhavna Seth’s full name is Sambhavna Surender Kumar Seth. We must have seen her on YouTube, in Big Boss, and in many bhojpuri songs. She had a lot of love for dance since childhood. From the very beginning, she wanted to become a heroine. To make a career, she went to Mumbai with her father and gave many auditions, but did not get work and came back to Delhi. She did not do any work for 1 year, then after gaining some confidence, she again came to Mumbai. Got a film after a lot of struggle. She has worked in songs of many big films but those songs did not become hits but everyone was quite impressed with her dance.
Then he got a chance to work in Bhojpuri songs. The first song became so famous that now she started getting a lot of work in the Bhojpuri industry. Time passed and she also appeared in many reality shows like Big Boss, Khatron ke khiladi and Desi Girl. Today she runs a YouTube channel named Sambhavna Seth Entertainment on which she posts vlogs.

Today Sambhavna will tell her life story through Josh Talks. So definitely watch this Hindi motivational video of Josh Talks.

Sambhavna Seth जी का पूरा नाम Sambhavna Surender Kumar Seth है. हमनें इन्हें YouTube पर, Big Boss में, और कई bhojpuri songs में देखा होगा. बचपन से ही इन्हें Dance से काफ़ी प्यार था. शुरू से ही ये एक Heroine बनना चाहती थीं. Career बनाने के लिए ये अपने पापा के साथ Mumbai गईं कई Auditions दिए लेकिन काम नहीं मिला और ये Delhi वापस आ गई. 1 साल इन्होंने कुछ काम नहीं किया फिर थोड़ा confidence gain करके ये फिर Mumbai आ गई. बहुत struggle के बाद एक film मिली. इन्होंने काफ़ी बड़ी films के songs में काम किया है लेकिन वो गाने hit नहीं हुए लेकिन इनके Dance से सब काफ़ी impressed थे. फिर इन्हें bhojpuri songs में काम करने का मौक़ा मिला. पहला गाना इतना famous हुआ कि अब इन्हें bhojpuri industry में काफ़ी काम मिलने लगा. समय बीतता गया और ये कई reality shows में भी आई जैसे Big Boss, Khatron ke khiladi और Desi Girl. आज ये Sambhavna Seth Entertainment नाम से एक YouTube channel चलाती हैं जिसपर ये vlogs डालती हैं. 

आज जोश Talks के माध्यम से Sambhavna जी सुनायेंगी अपनी Life story. तो जोश Talks की इस Hindi motivational video को पूरा ज़रूर देखें. 

#JoshTalksHindi #SambhavnaSethJoshTalks #SambhavnaSethEntertainment 

Josh Talks Hindi aims to inspire and motivate you by bringing to you the best Hindi motivational videos. What started as a simple conference is now a fast-growing media platform that covers the most innovative rags to riches success stories with speakers from every conceivable background, including entrepreneurship, women’s rights, public policy, sports, entertainment, and social initiatives. With 7 regional languages in our ambit, our stories and speakers echo one desire: to inspire action. Our goal is to unlock the potential of passionate young Indians from rural and urban areas by inspiring them to overcome the challenges they face in their careers or business and helping them discover their true calling in life. 

“ज़िंदगी में कुछ बड़ा करने के लिए जोश का होना बहुत ज़रूरी है.” 
इसी सोच के साथ एक शुरुआत हुई. देश के कोने-कोने से सबसे प्रेरणादायक कहानियों को चुनकर हर उस शख्स तक पहुंचाने की जो बड़े सपने देखता है. 
इसी सोच का नाम है जोश Talks. 
वो मंच जहां कई Role Models आते हैं और अपने जीवन की प्रेरणादायक कहानी हमारे साथ शेयर करते हैं. वो अपने जीवन के उन किस्सों को शेयर करते हैं जहां वो Fail हुए, उन्होंने गलतियां की, कई बार हिम्मत भी टूटी पर अपने लक्ष्य को हासिल करके ही माने. 

अगर दो शब्दों में कहा जाए, तो जोश Talks हम सबके लिए हमारे ‘बड़े भैय्या/बड़ी बहन’ की तरह है. 
जो हमेशा हमारे दोस्त बनकर हमारी बात सुनते हैं और हमें कुछ नया सिखाते हैं.
तो चलो, जोश के साथ हर Goal को हासिल करें. :)

और हां! अगर हमारे पास ऐसे लोगों की कहानियां हैं जिन्होंने अपनी मेहनत और हिम्मत के दम पर अच्छा मुकाम हासिल किया है. जिससे आज वो समाज के लिए एक Role Model बन गए हैं. 
तो, अभी लिखकर भेज देते हैं - speakers@joshtalks.com

► जोश Talks Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/JoshTalksHindi​ 
► जोश Talks Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/JoshTalksHi...

MTV Hustle returns with auditions for its next season. 
Your favourite rappers from Hustle 2.0 reunite to bring to you The Hustle Reunion song which is a celebration of their journey on season 2 of Hustle.  
And now it’s your chance to be a part of the next season of your favourite rap show. So come on, vibe on this banger with MC Square, Paradox, Gravity, Srushti Tawade, Wicked Sunny, Nazz, Spectra & Panther as they celebrate the magic of Hustle. 

India, Ab Tumhari Baari! Tayyar ho jao for the auditions of MTV Hustle 03- Represent.

Track: The Hustle Reunion 
Written and Performed by: @mc_square7000   @Paradoxhere  @gravitymusic  @Srushti_Tawade  @nazzmusic  @spectra_music  @buildingpanther  Wicked Sunny 
Additional Lyricis: @epriyer  
Composers: @ParimalShais 
Mix & Master- Kalmireddy Nikhil

For more updates, follow this season of Hustle on:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/mtvhustle/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/mtvhustle

From rage-­filled Barbarians with glorious mustaches to pyromaniac wizards, raise your own army and lead your clan to victory! Build your village to fend off raiders, battle against millions of players worldwide, and forge a powerful clan with others to destroy enemy clans.
PLEASE NOTE! Clash of Clans is free to download and play, however some game items can also be purchased for real money 

Also, under our Terms of Service and Privacy Policy, you must be at least 13 years of age to play or download Clash of Clans.
A network connection is also required.

FEATURES
- Build your village into an unbeatable fortress 
- Raise your own army of Barbarians, Archers, Hog Riders, Wizards, Dragons and other mighty fighters
- Battle with players worldwide and take their Trophies
- Join together with other players to form the ultimate Clan
- Fight against rival Clans in epic Clan Wars 
- Build 18 unique units with multiple levels of upgrades
- Discover your favorite attacking army from countless combinations of troops, spells, Heroes and Clan reinforcements 
- Defend your village with a multitude of Cannons, Towers, Mortars, Bombs, Traps and Walls
- Fight against the Goblin King in a campaign through the realm

snippet.description:

Tere Bin Episode 49 - [Eng Sub] - Yumna Zaidi - Wahaj Ali - Digitally Presented by Nisa BB Cream - 31st May 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Tere Bin Digitally presented by Nisa BB Cream

Meerab is an ambitious and beautiful young girl who wants to pursue higher studies. Her entire world revolves around her parents and she believes in them the most. Her strong and confident personality makes her stand against social injustices around her.

On the contrary, Murtasim hails from a powerful and influential family. He respects and values the morals and traditions of his family and refuses to let the family down.

Meerab’s life takes an unexpected turn when she finds out about her family’s decision regarding her and Murtasim’s life. Meerab’s hatred towards Murtasim continues to grow as a family secret from the past resurfaces. Coming from different backgrounds and mindsets, Murtasim begins to realize Meerab’s arrogant behaviour towards him and begins to consider her a challenge for himself. On the other hand, Meerab who is used to living her life on her own terms refuses to accept Murtasim’s family traditions and unnecessary social barriers.

Soon their lives go through a series of emotional sufferings and misunderstandings where it becomes difficult for them to coexist. Despite their hatred towards each other, will Meerab and Murtasim accept their true feelings or will the dynamics of ego and self-respect force them to stay apart?

Writer: Nooran Makhdoom
Director: Siraj ul Haq
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment

Cast :
Yumna Zaidi as Meerab
Wahaj Ali as Murtasim
Bushra Ansari as Salma

Fazila Qazi as Aneela
Farhan Ally Agha as Waqas
Seemi Pasha as Sabra

Haris Waheed
Agha Mustafa

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3787: Hum Dono Ki Haan Hai
--------------------------------------------------------
Pyaarelal decides to pick Kalpana after meeting with her parents, while Sapna's parents are waiting for his response. Babita and Madhavi advise Pyaarelal to accept Kalpana's proposal because they are unsure of Sapna's final decision. So Pyaarelal ultimately decides on Kalpana. When the marriage is restored, everyone rejoices. Sapna, on the other hand, agrees with the proposal. What would Pyaarelal's decision be now that both families have approved for him to be their son-in-law? Keep an eye out! 

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3787, 2 June 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

பாடல்வரிகள் :

சூலாயுதம் கொண்டு யம தூதர் வந்து என்னைச்
சூழ்ந்து கொண்டால் வேலாயுதா என்று
கூப்பிடுவேன் அந்த வேளைதனில் மாலான
வள்ளி தெய்வானை யொடு மயில் விட்டு இறங்கி
காலால் நடந்து வரவேணும் என் கந்தப்பனே

முருகா வேலுண்டு வினையில்லை
மயிலுண்டு பயமில்லை
குகனுண்டு குறைவில்லை மனமே
கந்தனுண்டு கவலையில்லை மனமே மனமே மனமே

வேல் முருகா மால் மருகா
வேல் முருகா வேல்
வேல் முருகா மா பழனி
வேல் முருகா வேல்

நீலகண்டன் நெற்றிக் கண்ணில்
நெருப்பு வடிவாகத் தோன்றி
நிருதர் குலத்தை அழித்த நிர்மலன் ... முருகன்

விழிகளொரு பன்னிரண்டு
உடையவனே என்று சொல்லி
விழிகளிலே நீர் பெருக்கி நின்றேன் ... முருகா

உலகமென்னும் கடல் தனிலே
உடல் என்னும் ஓடமது
உன்னடிக் கரை அடைய அருளுவாய் ... முருகா

ஓயாது ஒழியாது
உன் நாமம் சொல்பவர்க்கு
உயர் கதிதான் தந்திடுவாய் ... முருகா

கருணையே வடிவமான
கந்தசாமித் தெய்வமே உன்
கழலடியைக் காட்டி என்னை ஆளுவாய் ... கந்தனே

நெற்றியிலே நீறணிந்து
நெறியாக உனை நினைந்து
பற்றினேன் உள்ளமதில் உன்னடி ... முருகா

நெஞ்ச மதில் வஞ்சமின்றி
நிர் மலனே நின்னடியைத்
தஞ்சமென நெஞ்சமதில் எண்ணினேன் ... முருகா

ஆறுபடை வீட்டினிலே
ஆறுமுக வேலவனே
ஆதரித்து எனை ஆளும் ஐயனே ... முருகா

திருப்புகழைப் பாடி உந்தன்
திருவடியைக் கைதொழுது
திருவருளைப் பெற்றிட நான் வந்தேன் ... முருகா

கந்தர நுபூதி பாடி
கந்தனே உன் கழலடியைக்
கைதொழுது கரைசேர வந்தேன் ... முருகா

வேலவனே என்றுபாடி
வேண்டிடும் அடியவர்க்கு
வேண்டும் வரம் தந்திடுவான் பாருமே ... முருகா

மந்திரமும் தந்திரமும்
மருந்துமாக நின்ற உந்தன்
மலரடியைக் காணவேதான் வந்தேன் ... முருகா

தெள்ளு தினை மாவும்
தேனும் பரிந்தளித்த
வள்ளிக்கு வாய்த்தவனே ... முருகா

வடிவேலா என்று தினம்
வாழ்த்துகின்ற அடியவர்க்கு
கொடிய வினை தீர்த்திடுவான் பாருமே ... முருகா

பரங்குன்று செந்திலும்
பழனி மலை ஏரகம்
பலகுன்று பழமுதிரும் சோலையாம் ... முருகா

snippet.title: Meet India's Most RESPECTED Politician - Nitin Gadkari On Figuring Out 93 | Raj Shamani
snippet.description:
Co-presented to you by @MyGovIndia 

Order my first book 'Build, Don't Talk' here: https://amzn.eu/d/eCfijRu

Subscribe To Our Other YouTube Channels:-

https://www.youtube.com/@rajshamaniclips

https://www.youtube.com/@RajShamani.Shorts

--------------

Join us for an insightful conversation with Nitin Gadkari, an esteemed Indian politician and the current Minister of Road Transport and Highways of India, on our latest podcast episode! 🌟

In this engaging discussion, we delve into Mr. Gadkari's visionary approach to infrastructure development, sustainable transportation, and his unwavering commitment to transforming India's road network. As one of the key architects behind numerous ambitious projects, he shares valuable insights on building world-class highways, promoting electric mobility, and implementing innovative solutions to tackle the challenges of urban congestion and pollution.

Get ready to gain a deeper understanding of the transformative initiatives spearheaded by Mr. Gadkari, as he discusses the significance of renewable energy in transportation, the integration of smart technologies, and the promotion of alternative fuels. Discover how his innovative thinking and strategic planning are paving the way for a greener, more efficient, and digitally connected India.

Beyond infrastructure, we explore Mr. Gadkari's broader vision for economic growth, job creation, and the development of rural areas. Join us for this inspiring conversation with Nitin Gadkari, a dynamic leader who is shaping the future of India's transportation landscape. Tune in to gain valuable insights and be part of the journey towards a sustainable and prosperous nation. Don't miss out - subscribe to our channel and hit the notification bell to stay updated with our latest episodes!

-------------------------

🎧 Listen to Figuring Out Episode with Shri Nitin Gadkari On Spotify:

Raj Shamani is an Entrepreneur at heart that explains his expertise in Business Content Creation & Public Speaking. He has delivered 200+ speeches in 26+ countries. Udaariyaan | उड़ारियां | Ep. 704 & 705 | Recap

After learning about Nehmat's decision to marry Sartaj, Ekam kidnaps her in order to prevent the wedding. Meanwhile, Sartaj and Harleen become worried after noticing Nehmat's sudden disappearance from the house. Will they be able to find the truth?

Hailing from a small village in Punjab, the Sandhu family is driven by one obsession: to leave their sarson ke khet behind & migrate to Canada aka Kaneda! A cruel twist of fate, however, has different plans for the two sisters Tejo & Jasmine when the dashing Fateh comes into their lives. Will the three be able to fulfill their sapon ki Udaariyaan?

A cruel twist of fate, however, has different plans for the two sisters Tejo & Jasmine when the dashing Fateh comes into their lives. Will the three be able to fulfill their sapon ki Udaariyaan?

snippet.title: 7 Days Thali - हफ्ते मे 1दिन बनाती हूँ गेहूं की रोटी, बाकी दिन क्या बनता हैं चलो बताती हूँ Secretआज
snippet.description:
Aaj Masala Kitchen Me Ban Raha Hai 𝐇𝐚𝐟𝐭𝐞 𝐊𝐢 𝟔 𝐒𝐩𝐞𝐜𝐢𝐚𝐥 𝐓𝐡𝐚𝐥𝐢 𝐑𝐞𝐜𝐢𝐩𝐞. Healthy Aur Tasty Gluten-Free Recipe Banaiye Ek Khas Trick Se. 

#Vegthalirecipe #Ragirotirecipe #WeightlossRecipe #7DaysThali #MasalaKitchenThaliRecipe #MultigrainChapati #JowarKiRoti #ChawalRotiRecipe #RagiParatha #LessOilHealthyRecipe #trending 
----------------------------------------
👉𝐑𝐞𝐜𝐞𝐧𝐭 𝐔𝐩𝐥𝐨𝐚𝐝: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=kMzawKN94Dk

Please Follow Me On:
👍𝐅𝐚𝐜𝐞𝐛𝐨𝐨𝐤: https://www.facebook.com/masalakitchenrecipe
📸𝐈𝐧𝐬𝐭𝐚𝐠𝐫𝐚𝐦: https://www.instagram.com/masalakitchenbypoonam/

Subscribe Karein Humare 2nd YouTube Channel ko:
▶️𝐌𝐚𝐚 𝐘𝐞𝐡 𝐊𝐚𝐢𝐬𝐞 𝐊𝐚𝐫𝐮𝐧?: https://www.youtube.com/c/Maayehkaisekarun

🌐𝐖𝐞𝐛𝐬𝐢𝐭𝐞 𝐋𝐢𝐧𝐤 - https://www.poonamdevnani.com/
----------------------------------------
👉𝐑𝐄𝐋𝐀𝐓𝐄𝐃 𝐋𝐈𝐍𝐊𝐒:
Office 6 Tiffin Recipe
https://youtu.be/8FLvAP2tX4U

Tiffin Recipe For Whole Week
https://youtu.be/3lnvzhIgpfc

6 School Lunch Idea
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=-N2hTLODFjE

Raagi ke Papad
https://youtu.be/6XdfLXQYvho

Easy Sooji Papad Recipe
https://youtu.be/fTwpXZ2TA5c

Instant Dahi Vada Recipe
https://youtu.be/0LwnKmCjTg8
-------------------------------------
✍🏻𝗜𝗡𝗚𝗥𝗘𝗗𝗜𝗘𝗡𝗧𝗦:
 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟏:
* Water (पानी) - 1 Cup
* Sorghum Flour/Jowar Atta (ज्वार का आटा) - 1Cup
* Ghee (घी) - Some  
𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐:
* Water (पानी) - 2 Cup
* Oil (तेल) - Some
* Salt (नमक) - Some
* Ragi Flour/Nachni (रागी का आटा) - 1 Cup
* Boiled Potato (उबले आलू)
* Green Chilli (हरी मिर्च)
* Corainder Leaves (धनिया पत्ती)
𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟑:
Normal Wheat Flour Chapati
𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟒:
* Rice flour (चावल का आटा) - 1 Cup
* Water (पानी) - 1 Cup
𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟓:
* Rice
𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟔:
* Multigrain Flour (मल्टीग्रेन आटा) -  1 Cup
* Water (पानी) - 1 Cup

✍🏻𝐑𝐄𝐂𝐈𝐏𝐄:
𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟏 - 𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐉𝐨𝐰𝐚𝐫 𝐑𝐨𝐭𝐢, keep the pan on the flame & put Water & come to boil first. When the Water boiled then put Sorghum Flour/Jowar Atta to it. Mix well, cover & keep it for 5 minutes. Then knead the dough well else there will be cracks while patting roti. Finally, make chapati & enjoy with Dal, Bhindi, Curd & Sproud Salad. 

𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐 - 𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐑𝐚𝐠𝐢 𝐏𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐡𝐚, keep the pan on the flame & put Water & come to boil first. When the Water is boiled then put Ragi Atta & mix. Then knead the dough adding little water gradually to make firm and smooth dough. Then take a dough ball & fill the filling in it. Then flatten them with the fingers. Roast the Paratha & serve the Healthy Ragi Tawa Paratha Recipe along with Mix Dal, Dry Karele, Raita & Green Salad. 

𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟑 - 𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐑𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐑𝐨𝐭𝐢, keep the pan on the flame & put Water & come to boil first. When the Water boiled then put Rice Flour. Mix well, cover & keep it for 5 minutes. Then knead the dough well else there will be cracks while patting roti. Finally, make chapati & enjoy with Sabzi, Mango, Papad & Sproud Raita. 

𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟒 - 𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐑𝐢𝐜𝐞, wash some Rice and put it in pressure cooker. Add two cups of water along with a few drops of Oil/Ghee & Salt to it. 
Turn the heat to high. Wait for 3 steams and turn off the heat & release the pressure. Serve hot & enjoy with Chhole, Salad, Curd & Dry Arbi ki sabzi. 

𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟓 - 𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐌𝐮𝐥𝐭𝐢𝐠𝐫𝐚𝐢𝐧 𝐑𝐨𝐭𝐢, take a plate & put some Multigrain Flour & bind the dough by adding some water gradually. Cover & keep aside for some time. Then make Chapati & serve with Dal, Sabzi, Salad & Dahi Bhalla. In this way, 7 Days special thali will get ready easily. 
-----------------------------

 𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟏:
* Water (पानी) - 1 Cup
* Sorghum Flour/Jowar Atta (ज्वार का आटा) - 1Cup

𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐:
* Water (पानी) - 2 Cup

𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟑:
Normal Wheat Flour Chapati
𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟒:

𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟔:
* Multigrain Flour (मल्टीग्रेन आटा) -  1 Cup
* Water (पानी) - 1 Cup

✍🏻𝐑𝐄𝐂𝐈𝐏𝐄:
𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟏 - 𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐉𝐨𝐰𝐚𝐫 𝐑𝐨𝐭𝐢, keep the pan on the flame & put Water & come to boil first. When the Water boiled then put Sorghum Flour/Jowar Atta to it. Mix well, cover & keep it for 5 minutes. Then knead the dough well else there will be cracks while patting roti. Finally, make chapati & enjoy with Dal, Bhindi, Curd & Sproud Salad. 

𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟐 - 𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐑𝐚𝐠𝐢 𝐏𝐚𝐫𝐚𝐭𝐡𝐚, keep the pan on the flame & put Water & come to boil first. When the Water is boiled then put Ragi Atta & mix. Then knead the dough adding little water gradually to make firm and smooth dough. Then take a dough ball & fill the filling in it. Then flatten them with the fingers. Roast the Paratha & serve the Healthy Ragi Tawa Paratha Recipe along with Mix Dal, Dry Karele, Raita & Green Salad. 

𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟑 - 𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐑𝐢𝐜𝐞 𝐑𝐨𝐭𝐢, keep the pan on the flame & put Water & come to boil first. When the Water boiled then put Rice Flour. Mix well, cover & keep it for 5 minutes. Then knead the dough well else there will be cracks while patting roti. Finally, make chapati & enjoy with Sabzi, Mango, Papad & Sproud Raita. 

𝐃𝐚𝐲 𝟒 - 𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐑𝐢𝐜𝐞, wash some Rice and put it in pressure cooker. Add two cups of water along with a few drops of Oil/Ghee & Salt to it. 
Turn the heat to high. Wait for 3 steams and turn off the heat & release the pressure. Serve hot & enjoy with Chhole, Salad, Curd & Dry Arbi ki sabzi.

Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3786: Sapna Ya Kalpana?
--------------------------------------------------------
Pyaarelal, according to the astrologer, must choose his bride before 6 p.m. since it is a fortunate period for him. So Pyaarelal proclaims that he likes Sapna, and everyone waits for Sapna's response. The doorbell rings, and Taarak looks through the peephole to see if Alka and her parents have arrived. Sapna's parents interrogate them about the truth, and Taarak informs them. Sapna's parents are first upset, but when Anjali explains that the marriage bureau contacted them after their meeting was scheduled, they accept the situation. What happens next? Which girl will become Pyaarelal's bride?
 
Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3786, 1 June 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo 

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :
https://www.sonyliv.com/dplnk?schema=sony://asset/1000222332

Watch More Like This : https://www.youtube.com/starplus/videos


*About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

*About* 
------------

               Yeh kahani hai ek sanyukt parivaar mai rehnewale Modi khaandaan ki. Izzatdaar, ameer aur naamcheen hone ke bawajud, ghar ke sanskaar aur sanskriti hain inka saccha dhan. Iss ghar ko chalati hai choti bahu, Kokilaben jissey darte hain saare sadasya. Kokilaben ke bade bete, Ahem ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi se joh hai ek saaf dil ki siddhi saadhi, anpapdh ladki. Unke jethani ke bete, Jigar ki shaadi hojati hai Gopi ki behen, Raashi se joh hai bohot hi chaalaak aur nakhrel. 
              Raashi hamesha dikhati hai neecha Gopi ko aur karti hai uske liye mushkilen taiyaar. Par Gopi ka haath thama Kokilaben ne aur banaya ussey hoshiyaar. Iss saas-bahu ki jodi ne apne pyaar, dulaar aur balidaan se bandhe rakha hai Modi parivaar ko.

snippet.title: Debt ceiling explained in Hindi | American Economic Crisis | Abhi and Niyu
snippet.description:
In this video, Abhi and Niyu explain the Debt Ceiling crisis of USA and why America will never be like Sri Lanka.

#debtceiling #worldaffairs #abhiandniyu 

In our informative and engaging video, "Understanding the Debt Ceiling: Navigating Fiscal Challenges," we delve into one of the most critical aspects of economic governance: the debt ceiling. Join us on a journey through the complexities of national debt, government spending, and the mechanisms in place to manage these fiscal challenges.

With a clear and concise narrative, we break down the debt ceiling concept, explaining its purpose and implications. Our expert hosts provide a comprehensive overview of how the debt ceiling functions within the framework of a country's financial system and explore the practical effects it has on government operations and the economy at large.

As the video progresses, we explore the historical context behind the establishment of debt ceilings and how they have evolved over time. We shed light on the reasons governments may hit their debt limit and the consequences that can arise when the ceiling is breached. Our analysis includes the potential effects on financial markets, credit ratings, borrowing costs, and public trust in the government's fiscal responsibility.

Additionally, we examine the intricate relationship between the debt ceiling and the political landscape. Through case studies and real-world examples, we explore how debates and negotiations surrounding debt ceiling increases or suspensions often become contentious and polarizing. We discuss the various strategies employed by governments to address the debt ceiling and the potential implications for the economy and citizens.

Throughout the video, we present clear graphics, charts, and data visualizations to enhance understanding and illustrate the key concepts discussed. We ensure that even viewers without prior knowledge of economics or government finance can follow along and grasp the significance of the debt ceiling in the broader financial ecosystem.

Whether you are a student, a concerned citizen, or a professional seeking to expand your knowledge of economic governance, "Understanding the Debt Ceiling: Navigating Fiscal Challenges" offers valuable insights and a comprehensive overview of this critical aspect of fiscal policy. Join us on this informative journey and gain a deeper understanding of the debt ceiling's impact on national economies and everyday lives.

A video by Abhiraj Rajadhyaksha & Niyati Mavinkurve

About Us:
Abhi and Niyu is the fastest growing Indian educational YouTube channel. Abhi and Niyu are a husband-wife couple who believe in the power of our youth.

Abhi and Niyu started their page to talk about positive, impactful ideas and to inspire offline action from online content. It was a way to change the way our negative feeds operated and replace negative news with positive, action-oriented news that made some change.
